      "content": "I'm not a doctor, but I can tell you that your symptoms sound like you might have something more serious, like appendicitis, which requires immediate medical attention. Ibuprofen and codeine can be dangerous when combined, especially without a doctor's supervision. If you're in severe pain, you should seek medical help right away. In the meantime, try to rest and avoid eating until you can get evaluated.",
